ist生計根本弊多於利<br />\n特別係因為有聽spotify=支持正版嘅假像<br />\n想支持創作始終都係要實實際際比錢買歌</blockquote><br />\n香港有Indie 俾歌Spotify, moov 同騰訊果舊野播，三間夾埋收既錢都唔夠買份報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁無spotify,知名度低既artist唔見得幾易生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dd82ba66abf150067ccf3740820e022c434404","tid":192052,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>李嘉誠呢咁保守既商人都肯投資咁多科技野真係佩服<br />\n唔知邊個教佢咁多科技野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢負責俾錢姐，俾錢邊個係d「細」既睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估唔洗比佢睇咩</blockquote><br />\n睇份report 姐，你佩服佢班手下好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">做老細識用人重要過識做野</span>，李嘉誠睇人一定好準</blockquote><br />\n冇錯，用人勁已經夠，做野更叻都係跟order做野，用人勁係落order 果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n誠哥自己都好有心睇呢D科技野，之前有獨家訪問，佢話自己每日會用一粒鐘睇下科研新聞，例如AI呀個D<br />\n<br />\n所以佢一直都好肯比錢投資科研，譬如咩人造肉人造蛋"},{"pid":"e5f18e30d797a84d42d5942a2a1e1bdfae741b58","tid":192052,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82492371d464141ff59e8fccc14b426396ca40b1","tid":192052,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>李嘉誠呢咁保守既商人都肯投資咁多科技野真係佩服<br />\n唔知邊個教佢咁多科技野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢負責俾錢姐，俾錢邊個係d「細」既睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估唔洗比佢睇咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢旗下有個投資的team﹐每星期(定唔記得每月)﹐每個人都要出proposal﹐好詳細去推薦一間值得投資的新興市場公司<br />\n已經run左好多年係咁，好多冇特別報出黎的，都賺到笑</blockquote><br />\n一百單係蝕有3-4單係賺都賺返曬，如果好彩D的話一間（例如fb）都賺突有餘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nstartup世界正正就係10個project得一個成功，唔會單單包贏包賺，所以大部份香港人都唔肯投資落去，連個政府都係咁，唔係點會成日俾人話hitech hi野。<br />\n李嘉誠蝕嘅project當然唔會講但至少佢係香港少數有錢佬真係敢於投資落startup, 雖然佢間長實堅pk有份搞到香港變做地產港，但佢敢於投資startup無疑值得稱讚"},{"pid":"f7879a13a6fe822c0ec665005405b14ca050b23d","tid":192052,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc43346f9e1ec0584c9edc93a631564096e41b51","tid":192052,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2388c8946b6d2b3e7bf115d4ace7c6ed5889e65","tid":192052,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班友唔Join Spotify 呢Music Steaming Service 都唔見得會賺好多。<br />\n<br />\n跟本係世界變左。</blockquote><br />\n少少錢唔洗搵mp3咁煩，隻隻碟都有唔想要既歌，唔想硬食</blockquote><br />\nstreaming service唔係問題<br />\n問題係Spotify payout少到老母都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個營運模式基本上同出賤價請designer，然後話係比機會佢宣傳差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n網上資料話有七成係俾唱片公司同音樂人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢既分帳方式係一大塊餅所有音樂人按播放次數分<br />\n所以每人分到塊餅好細<a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/35644/BN-ARTICLE-35644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F35644%2FBN-ARTICLE-35644&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f7490412\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/35644/BN-ARTICLE-35644</a></blockquote><br />\n台灣報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/12/7/9861372/spotify-year-in-review-artist-payment-royalties\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2015%2F12%2F7%2F9861372%2Fspotify-year-in-review-artist-payment-royalties&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ef6dabc3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.theverge.com/2015/12/7/9861372/spotify-year-in-review-artist-payment-royalties</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@michaelcbrook/this-is-why-spotify-pays-so-little-how-to-fix-it-1e0c0e1ef860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40michaelcbrook%2Fthis-is-why-spotify-pays-so-little-how-to-fix-it-1e0c0e1ef860&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d24839c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@michaelcbrook/this-is-why-spotify-pays-so-little-how-to-fix-it-1e0c0e1ef860</a><br />\n基本上嗰七成幾絕大部分都係比top 1% artist同labels食晒<br />\n唔係紅到發紫嘅話靠佢開飯一個星期都未必捱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSpotify變成主要音樂消費途徑對知名度低嘅artist生計根本弊多於利<br />\n特別係因為有聽spotify=支持正版嘅假像<br />\n想支持創作始終都係要實實際際比錢買歌</blockquote><br />\n香港有Indie 俾歌Spotify, moov 同騰訊果舊野播，三間夾埋收既錢都唔夠買份報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁無spotify,知名度低既artist唔見得幾易生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntaylor swift屌spotify屌到咁，可能真係好仆街掛<br />\n無理由佢有錢都唔賺"},{"pid":"a9561db9fc89af369e14f9ad3ba57fea856fd9a2","tid":192052,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a942c7398260807dcbf19aa4ff5518734e19d014","tid":192052,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae9406ddc15256aaa2fe7314c6e9c0168d3a0845","tid":192052,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:11:37.000Z","msg":"轉用 music 👋🏻"},{"pid":"36ffc8d6f9485da40ad205300604dca0e9b2d2d7","tid":192052,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}